uctive and sustainable manner relationship builderi thrive on forging connections both within organizations and beyond i make a point of getting to know people understanding what drives them and what they are looking to achieve i integrate different perspectives while creating consensus around specific strategies and actions and i enjoy working with people of all backgrounds and levels of experience to develop and implement creative ideas grounded visionarygiven the rapid and turbulent change in healthcare strong leadership is required to provide vision build foundations and consolidate progress i offer fresh thinking combined with practical strategies to achieve tangible resultserfahrungdirector of regional operationsiora healthoktober  – heute  jahr  monategroßraum chicago und umgebungi joined iora for the opportunity to create a seamless care  insurance model with harken health a newly formed subsidiary of unitedhealthcare we use relationshipbased primary care to engage patients coordinate care improve outcomes and reduce unnecessary costs launching partnerships i relocated from new york to set up four primary care centers in chicago complete with new teams new products new facilities a new brand and a new organization my efforts entail significant coordination between harken centers in chicago and atlanta harken hq in minnetonka and iora hq in boston developing workflowsi am responsible for management operations and performance across the chicago market i routinely work through challenges with systems processes people and strategies my efforts focus largely on the following• clarifying roles responsibilities and expectations• identifying priorities and marshaling resources to address them • bolstering connectivity among different functions and locationscollaborating with providersi work closely with providers to solve complex problems and adapt strategies i help them balance the demands of daily operations with the need to drive clinical innovation topics includ