audit design and consulting training fulfilment and support ezio technology is in use in banks such as abn amro barclays and nordea barclaysedit as of july  more than one million barclays customers are using gemalto’s cryptographic smart card reader called pinsentry by barclays for strong authentication for online banking fino paytech limitededit in june  the financial information network and operations ltd fino paytech limited in india began deploying gemalto smart cards with biometric authentication to enable microbanking and the underbanked population in rural india security public sector egovernmentedit gemalto provides technology to the governments of more than  countries epassportsedit gemalto supplies electronic passports epassports solutions to the united states singapore czech republic denmark estonia france india italy latvia norway qatar poland portugal slovenia morocco sweden and turkey as of march  gemalto has provided technology to more than  million epassports making them the largest provider of epassport solutions with an estimated  percent market share in the united states gemalto is one of two vendors picked by the government printing office to supply their epassport program in  edriver’s licensesedit mexico’s licensing authority icv used gemalto’s smart card platform to issue the first edriver’s licenses to the city of monterrey nuevo león mexico in  gemalto expects to deliver more than  licenses to icv over a threeyear period gemalto secured a new contract to supply electronic card driver’s license to three additional mexican states in april  in december  gemalto began supplying sweden with edriver’s licenses that contain a transparent window in the polycarbonate structure aimed at enhanced physical security gemalto will supply sweden with  edriver’s licenses per year for three years eid citizen cardsedit in february  the portuguese mint and national printing office incm picked gemalto to provide their national eid citizen card gemalto provides the operating system the personalization system and applications the middleware and associated helpdesk services all portuguese citizens will ultimately carry these cards as their national id document ehealthcare cardsedit in september  gemalto delivered its  millionth ehealthcare card gemalto has delivered ehealthcare cards in algeria belgium china finland france germany mexico puerto rico slovenia the united kingdom and the united states in july allgemeine ortskrankenkasse aok a german health insurer also picked gemalto to supply and personalize  million ehealth insurance cards the cards contain emergency data such as blood group allergy alerts and ongoing treatments and eprescriptions egovernment idedit as of december  gemalto has provided  million common access cards to the united states department of defense for employee and contractor use transportationedit gemalto has provided contactless payment technology to a nationwide transport project in the netherlands and citywide projects in boston paris london são paulo and santiago gemalto has delivered more than  million transit cards internationally security and enterpriseedit gemalto supplies its enterprise services through valueadded resellers vars and systems integrators the company’s customers include barclays shell chevron pfizer boeing telia sonera schlumberger and microsoft in april  alternative technology began offering gemalto’s ondemand device administration service das through its network of  resellers in the united states and canada in april  envoy data corporation  began offering gemalto’s ondemand device administration service das through its network of it security specialized vars pfizeredit at pfizer  employees use gemalto smart cards as badges virchow krauseedit in july  gemalto began deploying protiva net dual tokens at virchow krause  company llp vk the th largest accounting firm in the united states microsoft partnershipedit microsoft employees worldwide use gemalto net smart card technology embedded in their corporate badge to enable access to microsoft’s own information systems in june  gemalto announced that instant badge issuance ibi a solution that works directly with microsoft active directory and identity lifecycle manager ilm to load digital certificates directly onto the smart card at microsoft’s heroes happen here event in february  gemalto and microsoft demonstrated the only net smart card technology with support built into microsoft windows server  in november  gemalto made its net smart card protiva strong authentication server and related protiva credential devices and other windows smart card frameworkcompatible products available for live simulation at the microsoft partner solutions center on microsoft corp’s redmond washington campus in november  gemalto attained gold certified partner status in the microsoft partner program in  gemalto organized a microsoftsponsored contest securetheweb for the best new development in secure personal devices for web services such as smart cards and onetime passwords otps citrix systems partnershipedit in december  gemalto announced that its protiva platform were recognized by citrix systems as compatible with the citrix access gateway this followed a previous announcement earlier in january  that gemalto’s net and protiva solutions were recognized by citrix systems as compatible with its products in january  gemalto was named a finalist for  solution partner of the year by citrix systems verisignedit in february  gemalto announced that its network identity manager nim for online security would support the verisign identity protection vip network security breachesedit according to documents leaked by edward snowden nsas and gchqs mobile handset exploitation team infiltrated gemaltos infrastructure to steal sim authentication keys allowing them to secretly monitor mobile communications gchq codenamed the program dapino gamma the secret gchq document leaked by snowden also claimed the ability to manipulate billing records to conceal their own activity and having access to authentication servers to decrypt voice calls and text messages snowden stated that when the nsa and gchq compromised the security of potentially billions of phones gg encryption relies on the shared secret resident on the sim they not only screwed the manufacturer they screwed all of us because the only way to address the security compromise is to recall and replace every sim sold by gemalto the breach subsequently refueled suspicions against gemalto chairman alex j mandl given his role in the cia venture capital firm inqtel gchq and nsa declined to comment on the matter gemalto issued a press release on february   saying there were reasonable grounds to believe that an operation by nsa and gchq probably happened but denying that the government agencies gained access to any authentication keys partnershipsedit key partners of gemalto include wipro prodapt maya sendum unique computing solutions symphony teleca bing kore west etc see alsoedit charliecard gemalto mm referencesedit  a b c d e f annual report  gemalto   the endangered sim card the economist november     gemalto applies for a dual listing on nyse euronext amsterdam wwwgemaltocom retrieved  june    corporate brochure  gemalto   page not found – connected world connectedworldmagcom retrieved  june    newsroom netsizecom  october  retrieved  june    gemaltos earning conference retrieved    gsm world statistics archived from the original on  august  retrieved  november    mckool smith represents gemalto in patent infringement lawsuit over android gemalto mckool smith    digital security company gemalto loses patent fight against android ars technica    profil société de gemalto abcbourse nyseeuronext and quanthouse retrieved  february    frost  sullivan awards gemalto for its innovative solutions in mobile contactless technologies retrieved  november    gemalto pioneers sim reactivation retrieved    rogers wireless joins rbc and visa in mobi